<number box="[1273,1315,800,824]" pageId="7" pageNumber="197" value="8.5" valueMax="9.0" valueMin="8.0">8–9</number>
long erect bristles along inner margin, claws and ventral arolium of middle tarsal segment II leaf-like structure inserted subapically; hind femora stout and narrowed toward both ends, hind tibiae straight and longer than middle tibiae; length of leg segments (trochanters, femora, tibiae and tarsi): fore leg: 
