<number box="[991,1043,1340,1364]" pageId="7" pageNumber="197" value="0.18">0.18</number>
); forewings mainly blackish brown except basal part, whitish, tip slightly surpassing abdominal apex, hemelytron with dark veins; other characters as in apterous male.
</paragraph>
