, about 
<number box="[345,394,1556,1581]" pageId="7" pageNumber="197" value="1.65">1.65</number>
times head length, antennae about 
<number box="[787,836,1556,1580]" pageId="7" pageNumber="197" value="0.42">0.42</number>
times as long as body, length of antennal segments I– IV: 
<number box="[196,248,1591,1616]" pageId="7" pageNumber="197" value="0.16">0.16</number>
, 
<number box="[262,314,1592,1616]" pageId="7" pageNumber="197" value="0.18">0.18</number>
